parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unavailability of parts for the airbag recall repair can lead to a potential safety risk, as the airbags may not deploy properly in the event of an accident, increasing the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: None
as the issue is related to the unavailability of parts for the recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of airbags to deploy in the event of an accident can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in an accident
seat belt pretensioners did not engage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety-critical systems to malfunction, including airbags, lane detection, crash detection, and backup indicators, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The audio system
blinkers
lane detection
crash detection
back up indicators
OnStar
and other sound-related systems do not work; the radio randomly shuts off and reboots; the lower controls (heated seats
gate lift
etc.) do not work; the turn signal noise goes in and out; the tachometer and speedometer are impacted.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag and Side Detection System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and side detection system can cause accidents or injuries by failing to deploy airbags in the event of a crash or by providing false warnings.
symptoms: The airbag light is on; the side detection system light is on; the airbag system is not functioning properly; the side detection system is not functioning properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the cooling system can cause accidents or injuries by causing the engine to overheat, leading to engine failure or fire.
symptoms: The AC breaks and freon sprays through the vents; an abnormal odor of fumes emitting into the interior of the vehicle when the vent controls are used from A/C to heat.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the body and trim system can cause accidents or injuries by compromising the structural integrity of the vehicle.
symptoms: The rear door will not stay closed; the rear door opens while driving; the locks lock
unlock
and relocate randomly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or lock, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel is hard to turn
the steering wheel locks
a grinding or squealing noise is heard when turning the wheel
a burning smell is present
the vehicle vibrates or shimmies at highway speeds
the blind spot warning light stays continuously lit.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack and pinion can cause the steering wheel to become difficult to turn or lock, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel is hard to turn
the steering wheel locks
a grinding or squealing noise is heard when turning the wheel
cracks and screeches are heard coming from the steering rack when turning the wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electronic power steering sensor can cause the power steering system to malfunction, leading to a loss of control of the vehicle, which can result in accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The blind spot warning light stays continuously lit
the power steering is completely out
the vehicle is almost undeliverable.
